- id: substack-2026-07-25
  scheduled_at: "2026-07-25T08:00:00+10:00"
  platforms: [substack]
  title: "AI for Aussie Small Business: What Actually Works"
  body: |
    Most AI tools are built for enterprise budgets. I spent the last year building six practical tools for Australian small businesses — tradies, cafés, clinics, and shops.

    Three are live today: TaxFlowAI for accounting firms, LocalMate for local business automation, and CrewRoster for shift crews.

    Read more and watch the demos: https://crewcircle.com.au

- id: linkedin-taxflowai-2026-07-28
  scheduled_at: "2026-07-28T12:00:00+10:00"
  platforms: [linkedin]
  body: |
    Accountants: how long do you spend chasing ATO references?

    TaxFlowAI gives you cited answers from ATO rulings, determinations, and legislation. Upload an ATO letter and draft a response in minutes.

    Built for Australian tax professionals.

